707202f-a.title: Brooklyn: Vermont St. - Atlantic Ave.
707202f-a.text:
Vermont Street, west side, north of Atlantic Ave. The Ardley Palace
(an amusement hall) on the S.W. corner is partly visible because of the Loug
Island R.R. structure.
April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
